---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About -Todd Hainsworth" description="About Todd Hainsworth, Senior Software Engineer at Aligent.">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <section class="about">
    <p>
      Hi! I'm Todd 👋 I'm a Software Engineer from Adelaide, South Australia!
    </p>

    <p>
      I work a lot within the microservice space.
      Most of my work involves designing, prototyping and delivering bespoke integrations between
      ecommerce solutions, ERPs and PIMs.
    </p>


    <p>
      I care about building things that are fit for purpose - not over-engineered, not under-built.
      I believe it's important to ship something that works, then refine it often with real feedback
      from both non-technical and technical stakeholders.
    </p>

    <h2>What I value</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Diverse teams</strong> - different backgrounds and perspectives produce better outcomes.
        Homogeneous teams have blind spots.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>All ideas considered</strong> - the best solutions often come from unexpected directions.
        An environment where people feel safe to contribute ideas is one where good ideas actually surface.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fit for purpose, refined often</strong> - getting something workable in front of people early
        beats perfect solutions delivered late. Iterate from there.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Outside of work</h2>
    <p>
      When I'm not writing code, I'm usually reading or thinking about electric vehicles.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: -0.5rem;
  }

  .about ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about li {
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
